          <li>When in doubt, gift cards or treats work well</li>
          <li>Wrap it nicely - presentation matters!</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="reminder-box">
        <strong>ğŸ¤« Remember:</strong> Keep this assignment SECRET until the reveal on December 22nd!
